external_games.name: Warlord of the Karui Supporter Pack

name: Path of Exile: Warlord of the Karui Supporter Pack
summary: The Warlord of the Karui Supporter Pack contains Early Access to Path of Exile 2, four Armour Sets, four Back Attachments, a Finisher Effect, five Hideout Decorations, eight Weapon Skins, five Pets, a Weapon Effect, a Level-up Effect, a Hideout, a portal Effect, four Portrait Frames, four Forum Titles, four Badges, and 2200 Points.
